title: Omar Wasow on Violent vs. Non-Violent Protests, Plus Katie and Matt on Trump's Rally
description:
Omar Wasow, assistant professor of politics at Princeton, joins the show to discuss his paper on protest tactics and 'Agenda Seeding,' and the polarized reaction it's received. Matt and Katie analyze a scene from Delaware involving a manly encounter with a shark.
